name: 杰德·马
introduction: Jade Ma is an English actress based between Canada and England.She was born in 1997 in Hong Kong to a British father and Chinese mother. At 17, she moved to the UK to train at the Guildford School of Acting.Ma made her professional TV acting debut in the 2018 Christmas comedy film Surviving Christmas with the Relatives as Soon while also rehearsing for the UK/International Tour of Miss Saigon. In 2019, she was cast in the upcoming film Black Widow. She can now be seen starring as Sky Tyler in the recently released Netflix original series Zero Chill.
